Iva Denoo, the Ghanian Chargé d' Affaires in Nigeria, has been summoned over the demolition of the Nigerian High Commission in Ghana.Some armed men had stormed the Nigerian diplomatic building in Ghana and demolished several parts of the favility under construction. 





